text: Kientzheim was a commune in the Haut-Rhin department in north-eastern France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune Kaysersberg- Vignoble.Arrêté 14 July 2015 ==References== * INSEE Category:Former communes in Haut-Rhin Category:2016 disestablishments in France
title: Kientzheim
